你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "正确识别用户意图并路由到营销规划阶段",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "file": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py"
        },
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "file": "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "intent_recognition 阶段的意图分类逻辑或模型未能将用户输入（包含“NBEV目标”、“增加理财师”、“优化产品方案”）识别为营销规划意图，错误地分类为“其他意图”（intent=4001），并直接路由到 non_agent 阶段，导致后续规划流程无法启动。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0]",
          "field": "intent",
          "value": "4001"
        },
        {
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0]",
          "field": "stage",
          "value": "non_agent"
        },
        {
          "source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition",
          "actual_stage": "non_agent",
          "expected_stage": "intent"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_recognition",
          "file": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "与意图识别错误直接相关，intent_recognition 阶段输出了不符合 expected_stage 的 stage 值（non_agent 而非 intent），违反合约。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage",
          "value": "non_agent"
        },
        {
          "source": "reference_contract",
          "expected_stage": "intent"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "intent_recognition",
      "file": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py"
    },
    {
      "stage": "intent_recognition",
      "file": "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py"
    },
    {
      "stage": "intent_recognition",
      "module": "意图分类模型/配置"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "intent_recognition 阶段未能正确识别营销规划意图，错误地将业务诉求归类为“其他意图”（intent=4001），导致 stage 输出为 non_agent 而非 reference contract 要求的 intent，进而造成整个 planning 链路无法进入需满足的业务阶段，所有下游阶段（field_clarification、planning_function 等）均无法生成有效卡片。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "type": "actual_intent_code",
      "value": "4001",
      "source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent"
    },
    {
      "type": "actual_stage",
      "value": "non_agent",
      "source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage"
    },
    {
      "type": "expected_stage_contract",
      "value": "intent",
      "source": "reference_contract"
    },
    {
      "type": "execution_stage_probe_discrepancy",
      "actual_stage": "non_agent",
      "expected_stage": "intent",
      "source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition"
    },
    {
      "type": "planning_output_probe_stage_match",
      "value": false,
      "source": "planning_output_probe"
    },
    {
      "type": "empty_card_result",
      "card_count": 0,
      "source": "planning_function"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

